## ✨ Key Features

| Feature | Description |
|---|---|
| **Hybrid Search** | Combines dense embeddings (OpenAI `text-embedding-3-small`) with sparse BM25 for maximum recall |
| **Cohere Re-ranking** | Re-ranks top-20 candidates to top-5 using cross-encoder for precision |
| **Source Attribution** | Every answer includes document source, page number, and relevance score |
| **Sub-2s Latency** | Async FastAPI with connection pooling keeps P95 response time under 2 seconds |
| **RAGAS Evaluation** | Built-in evaluation suite measuring faithfulness, answer relevance, and context precision |
| **Dockerized** | Single `docker-compose up` to spin up the full stack locally |
| **Streaming Responses** | FastAPI SSE endpoint streams tokens as they're generated |
| **Metadata Filtering** | Filter retrieved documents by date, category, or source before re-ranking |

