## ⚙️ Setup & Installation

### Prerequisites

- Python 3.10+
- Docker & Docker Compose (optional)
- API keys: OpenAI, Pinecone, Cohere

### 1. Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/reshma-katta/rag-hybrid-search.git
cd rag-hybrid-search
```

### 2. Create virtual environment

```bash
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate        # macOS/Linux
# venv\Scripts\activate         # Windows
```

### 3. Install dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 4. Configure environment variables

```bash
cp .env.example .env
```

Edit `.env` with your API keys:

```env
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
PINECONE_API_KEY=...
PINECONE_ENVIRONMENT=us-east-1
PINECONE_INDEX_NAME=rag-hybrid-index
COHERE_API_KEY=...
```

### 5. Run with Docker (recommended)

```bash
docker-compose up --build
```

The API will be available at `http://localhost:8000` and the Streamlit UI at `http://localhost:8501`.

